T1  - On the Number of State Variables in Options Pricing
AU  - Li, Gang
AU  - Zhang, Chu
Y1  - 2010/09/03
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1222
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.1100.1222
